channel.title: [Best Exion's] Uncalled Attack [Project Insanity]
channel.description:
[center][size=12pt][b]Best Exion's you'll ever use![/b][/size][/center] [center][b][size=14pt]I removed the Quest Tab voting! It's an easy add though[/size][/b][/center]
[b]Source Link:[/b] http://www.mediafire.com/?u6ie4snnocr642j [b]Client Link:[/b] http://www.mediafire.com/?u4smbsoyvxz7534
[u][b]Features:[/b][/u] -100% Barrows effects -Fixed turmoil -Basic NPC clipping -Edited Barrows minigame -Added PK points -Added a PkP shop -Added a Barrows shop [b]-Added the Curse Prayers[/b] -Edited Quest Tab [s]-Added a Quest Tab voting method[/s] -Added basic Firemaking -Mass edited the Firemaking code -Better login methods -Added vengence -Edited the trading method -Added ::pure and ::master commands -Added repeating message -Edited starter -Fixed duping -Added an economy reset (emergencies only) [b]-Fixed the leech prayers [Curse prayers][/b] -Added Draynor NPC thieving -Fixed Falador -Added donor ranks -Mod information NPC -Fixed mute command -A fixed ::noclip command whether they add it to the client or not -Edited the hit system -Fixed duping methods -Fixed the Jad minigame -Highscores (shows only #1)
[hr] [u][b]More Features:[/b][/u] Red = Not Started Orange = working on Green = Completed
Jad minigame Basic NPC clipping [s]Quest Tab voting method[/s] Firemaking Curse Prayers Perfect magic Perfect melee Perfect Ranging Perfect PvE Perfect PvP Perfect Fishing Perfect Woodcutting Sweets Skillcape Emotes Perfect Fight Pits Zamorak Boss 474 anims load from the Cache Fullscreen 474 GFX load from cache Item degrading Sea Troll Queen Giant Mole BarrelChest Vengence Pk Points PkP Shop SoulSplit Mod Information NPC NPC Thieving No Dupes Highscores [hr]
So you can see that I've done quite a bit in just a few weeks. I hope that I could add plenty more updates in the future.

[quote=“James_Akins, post:23, topic:381051”]Okay not to be the first hateful post but I just had to point this shit out.

  1. “I wouldn’t ruin a 317 by adding new hit marks and bars”, though, you added the thing that ruined RuneScape: Turmoil

  2. The turmoil is bad, look at the fucking animation on that shit, WHY add it if you don’t have the right fucking animations anyway?

  4. This looks like a normal PI

  5. Wtf, why did you make a fucking gif of you opening a shop?

  6. Wtf, why did you make a gif of you eating frog legs, you act like that’s an accomplishment. Search “potions.java” search “385”(I believe that’s the shark code) copy and paste with frog legs ID…

  7. Okay, you showed a picture of turmoil about 5 fucking times now. Of course it raises your fucking damage, what else is it going to do?

  8. You added a FUCKING NPC just to explain to not fuck with mods, or something?

  9. Nice barrows. L0l?

  10. What the fucking ballsack, your source is 20MB

  11. Everything on here IS on 90% of servers (The godwars, the dueling, etc.)

  12. “Har har we got werkin’ messiges dat tells da player 2 vote n spams u up!!”

  13. What the fuck why do you have like 5 pictures of you doing skills that were ALREADY in PI?

  14. Not that I’d waste my time downloading this, but I doubt it has NPC clipping

  15. Don’t even put no dupes, I guarantee I’d be able to dupe on this

  16. MoparScape has a community of a bunch of 8 year olds, but I guess I can’t complain because R-S is full of a bunch of kids who think they’re better than everyone because they can press TAB in their code or some bullshit, and R-L(google) is just a bunch of faggots

  17. Don’t even get me started on your fucking arrangement of shit, reminds me of the Mopar toplist, where the kid says “PERFECT ECONOMY DROP PARTIES EVERY 5 MINUTES” I know this is a download but not an advertisement, but the organization reminds me of it.

  18. I’m pissed because some people spend fucking weeks coding shit and it doesn’t get respect, then some noob comes and releases some big pile of horse shit and gets everyone like “AMG AWEZOM SORCE BRO!!”, no, that’s not directed to myself, the only shit I released on this account took me 2 days to code, yet it had more added than this, still. Honestly if I was MITB, I’d go on the fucking toplist right now and permanently ban in every way possible every fucking kid that releases bullshit, so when people actually spend time making something that’s great, they actually get somewhere instead of having all the fucking kids leaching PI and DSPK and iHybrid and all that take all the fucking players, so they can see some real RSPS, they don’t want some fucking bullshit like this.

  19. I’m just in LOVE with your ‘goals’ you have. How about I rename what the colors mean: Already in PI Haven’t started but I’m planning on trying (lol jk I have no idea how) Never going to add just wanted to put something for people to look forward to

  20. Whoa!! Quick chat? Never seen that one before. Ohlawd…

  21. Workin’ PK points! Not like any other source has that :trollface:

  22. Best Exions I’ll ever use? Who said I’m using it? Because I’m definitely not

  23. Are you fucking retarded? Picture explains itself.

Thank you.[/quote]
